fluid-milk%22%3Etheir%0Ainformation%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20National%20Fluid%20Milk%20Processor%20Promotion%20Program%0A(%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FNational_Fluid_Milk_Processor_Promotion_Program%22%3EWikipedia%3C%2Fa%3E)%0Ahad%20annual%20revenues%20of%20approximately%20%24103%20million%20in%202012%0A%0A(%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.permanent.org%2Fp%2Farchive%2F0agp-0000%2F0agp-001o%2F1133837%2Frecord%2F0agp-001p%22%3Ecopy%0Aof%20the%202012%20report%3C%2Fa%3E).%0A%3C!--%20Also%20available%20in%20this%20directory%20as%20%22.%2F2012-dairy-report.pdf%22%20--%3E%0A%0AThey%20use%20this%0Ato%20fund%20various%20marketing%20efforts%2C%20including%20a%20couple%20of%20ad%20campaigns%2C%20among%0Aother%20things.%20Clearly%2C%20if%20these%20guys%20wanted%20it%2C%20they%20could%20afford%20to%20buy%20the%0Adomain.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20have%20an%20official%20link%20for%20the%20California%20Milk%20Processor%20Board%2C%0Abut%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22innovator-spring99.html%22%3Ethis%20article%20in%20the%0A%3Ci%3EUC%20Davis%20Innovator%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%201999%20their%20revenues%20were%20a%20more%20modest%0A%2427%20million%20a%20year%2C%20which%20they%20use%20for%20the%20%22got%20milk%3F%22%20ad%20campaign%20among%0Aother%20things.%20Maybe%20it'd%20be%20a%20bit%20more%20of%20a%20stretch%20for%20them%20compared%20to%0Atheir%20national%20counterpart%2C%20but%20they%20could%20afford%20the%20domain%20too%20if%20they%0Awanted%20it%20badly%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Ctable%20class%3D%22footer%22%3E%0A%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctd%3ESite%20copyright%20%C2%A9%201994%E2%80%932024%20Dan%20Bornstein.%20All%20rights%20reserved.%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22%2F%22%3Emilk.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20%2F%20value%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%0A%0A%0A%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fhtml%3E"
